data.description: PRICE ADJUSTMENT!! Welcome to 512 Crystal Hill Court in Birch Creek Ridge. This 3 bedroom and 2 full bath home has fresh paint throughout, new vinyl plank floors and carpet. The roof was installed in 2021. Heating and cooling updated in 2017. The home features a vaulted living room, beautiful open sun room with access to the back patio, breakfast area with separate dining and updated toilets. Large primary bedroom with a vaulted ceiling and en suite with garden tub and stand up shower. Schedule your showing today!
